    <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Join the Rebellion: Arm Solos Against Insurance Giants</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
            We're not building software. We're fueling a movement.
        </p>
        
        <div class="highlight">
            <p>
                Solo attorneys are bleeding $58K per case because insurance companies have Colossus (11 million settlement database). 
                We're building the equalizer. If that fires you up, keep reading.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <p style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A1A;">
            Intake that never sleeps. Drafts in 90 seconds. <strong>Settle™</strong> — the co-op engine exposing $58K lowballs with attorney-sourced data.
        </p>
        
        <p>
            Zero AI. Zero PHI risks. Blockchain-verified. Bootstrapped in Dubai for global firepower and attorney-first pricing.
        </p>
        
        <p>
            Founded by <strong>Afghan S. Yasha Ullah Khan</strong> — 34 years scaling Microsoft/Oracle/Cisco empires — we're founder-owned, VC-free, 
            and laser-focused on helping PI solos reclaim what insurance companies are stealing.
        </p>
        
        <p style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #0A2463; margin-top: 40px;">
            We're small, fierce, and growing.
        </p>
        
        <p>
            If you're tired of corporate bloat and ready to build tools insurers hate, let's talk.
        </p>
        
        <div class="quote-box">
            <p>"Working here feels like co-owning the future of justice."</p>
            <p class="quote-author">— Early Team Member (Engineer, Remote)</p>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Our Vow to You</h2>
        
        <div class="values-grid">
            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-icon">⚡</div>
                <h3>Impact First</h3>
                <p>Every line of code recovers real money for real attorneys. You'll see the direct results of your work.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-icon">🌍</div>
                <h3>Remote Global</h3>
                <p>Dubai HQ, but talent anywhere. Async-first. No offices. Work from wherever you thrive.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-icon">🚀</div>
                <h3>Bootstrapped Freedom</h3>
                <p>No VC deadlines. Build for decades, not exits. We're attorney-first, not investor-first.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-icon">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</div>
                <h3>Family First</h3>
                <p>Kids sick? Take the day. No guilt. We measure output, not hours logged.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Open Roles (Q3 2026 Hiring)</h2>
        
        <p style="text-align: center; background: #FFF9E6; padding: 24px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #78350F;">
            We're selective. <strong>11 hires/year max.</strong> Founding-team vibe.
        </p>
        
        <!-- ROLE 1: Senior FSM Engineer -->
        <div class="role-card">
            <h3>💻 Senior FSM Engineer (Remote, Full-Time)</h3>
            <p><strong>Mission:</strong> Harden Benjamin's deterministic core. Scale Settle™ queries to 1M/month. Build zero-knowledge architecture that attorneys can defend to the Bar.</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 24px;"><strong>You're a fit if:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>5+ years Python, FastAPI, Redis, PostgreSQL</li>
                <li>You've built FSM workflows or deterministic systems</li>
                <li>Blockchain curiosity (OpenTimestamps, immutable audit trails)</li>
                <li>You <strong>hate AI hype</strong> and prefer rock-solid rule-based systems</li>
                <li>You've built fintech, healthtech, or other regulated tech</li>
                <li>You want to build tech that fights for the underdog</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 24px;"><strong>What you'll work on:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Deterministic intake workflows (28 edge cases, zero AI)</li>
                <li>Settle™ query engine (match 147 similar settlements in <50ms)</li>
                <li>Zero-knowledge data pipelines (Bar-compliant, blockchain-backed)</li>
                <li>Real-time analytics dashboards for law firms</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- ROLE 2: Compliance Counsel -->
        <div class="role-card">
            <h3>⚖️ Bar Compliance Counsel (Part-Time, U.S.-Based)</h3>
            <p><strong>Mission:</strong> Bar-proof every feature. Draft compliance certificates. Advise on ABA Model Rules, state Bar regulations, and attorney advertising ethics.</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 24px;"><strong>You're a fit if:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Licensed attorney (active Bar membership required)</li>
                <li>Deep knowledge of ABA Model Rules and state Bar ethics</li>
                <li>You understand attorney confidentiality, UPL risks, and advertising rules</li>
                <li>Detail-oriented and can translate legal requirements into technical guardrails</li>
                <li>You care about protecting solo attorneys from Bar sanctions</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 24px;"><strong>What you'll work on:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Audit every TrueVow feature for Bar compliance</li>
                <li>Draft blockchain certificates for attorney audit trails</li>
                <li>Write compliance documentation for 50 state Bar associations</li>
                <li>Advise on zero-knowledge architecture and PHI handling</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- ROLE 3: Customer Success Warrior -->
        <div class="role-card">
            <h3>🎯 Customer Success Warrior (Remote, Full-Time)</h3>
            <p><strong>Mission:</strong> Onboard 11 law firms/week. Turn attorney feedback into features. Build the Founding Member community into a movement.</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 24px;"><strong>You're a fit if:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Ex-PI paralegal, law student, or attorney (legal background strongly preferred)</li>
                <li>Empathetic, patient, and a great teacher</li>
                <li>You understand attorney pain (Bar compliance, missed leads, lowball settlements)</li>
                <li>Data-driven (you measure retention, not just "customer happiness")</li>
                <li>You want to help attorneys win, not just "close support tickets"</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 24px;"><strong>What you'll work on:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Onboard solo attorneys and small firms (white-glove service)</li>
                <li>Train them on Benjamin, Settle™, and analytics dashboards</li>
                <li>Collect feedback and translate into product features</li>
                <li>Build Founding Member community (webinars, Q&As, success stories)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- ROLE 4: Growth Hacker -->
        <div class="role-card">
            <h3>📈 Growth Hacker (Remote, Full-Time)</h3>
            <p><strong>Mission:</strong> Fill 2,100 Founding Member spots. Build viral loops for Settle™ contributions. Drive attorney referrals.</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 24px;"><strong>You're a fit if:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>SEO/PPC wizard with legal tech experience</li>
                <li>You understand attorney buying behavior (they're skeptical, compliance-worried)</li>
                <li>Data-driven (you measure ROI, not vanity metrics)</li>
                <li>You've built referral loops, viral mechanisms, or co-op growth strategies</li>
                <li>You hate "growth at all costs" — you care about <strong>profitable, sustainable growth</strong></li>
            </ul>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 24px;"><strong>What you'll work on:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>SEO strategy (rank for "settlement database", "intake automation", etc.)</li>
                <li>PPC campaigns (Google Ads for PI attorneys)</li>
                <li>Viral referral loops (Partner Program, Affiliate Program)</li>
                <li>Settle™ co-op growth (incentivize settlement contributions)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- ROLE 5: Content Warrior -->
        <div class="role-card">
            <h3>✍️ Content Warrior (Legal Tech & Thought Leadership)</h3>
            <p><strong>Mission:</strong> Write content that positions TrueVow as the authority on fighting insurance lowball tactics. Educate attorneys on settlement data, Colossus, and negotiation strategies.</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 24px;"><strong>You're a fit if:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>You're a great storyteller (legal background is a plus)</li>
                <li>You can explain complex legal/tech concepts in plain English</li>
                <li>You understand attorney pain (Colossus, lowball settlements, Bar compliance)</li>
                <li>You want to write content that actually helps attorneys win cases, not just SEO fluff</li>
                <li>You can write long-form guides, blog posts, and case studies</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 24px;"><strong>What you'll work on:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Blog posts (e.g., "How Insurance Companies Use Colossus to Lowball You")</li>
                <li>Settlement guides (e.g., "Average PI Settlements by County")</li>
                <li>Case studies (how attorneys used TrueVow to win more)</li>
                <li>Thought leadership (fight insurance hegemony narrative)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Why Join TrueVow?</h2>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h3>🔥 Mission You Can Believe In</h3>
            <p>
                You're not building "engagement features" or "growth hacks." You're building tools that help solo attorneys fight $50 billion insurance databases.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Real impact:</strong> Customer Success sees attorneys capture leads they would've missed. Engineers see code help attorneys settle for $85K instead of $27K. 
                Compliance specialists prevent Bar sanctions before they happen.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                You'll know your work matters. That's rare in tech.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h3>🌍 Global Team, Remote-First</h3>
            <p>
                <strong>Our team is spread across:</strong> Dubai (operations), Pakistan (engineering), London (compliance), Toronto (customer success), U.S. (legal).
            </p>
            <p>
                We don't care where you live. We care that you're excellent at what you do and aligned with our mission.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Work from anywhere (as long as you overlap 4 hours with U.S. Eastern Time for key meetings)</li>
                <li>Async-first communication (Slack/Loom, not 6 hours of Zoom calls)</li>
                <li>Flexible hours (we measure output, not time logged)</li>
                <li>Annual team meetups (Dubai or U.S., all expenses paid)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h3>💪 Bootstrapped = Freedom</h3>
            <p>
                We're <strong>NOT VC-funded</strong>. That means:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>No board pressuring us to "monetize attorney data"</li>
                <li>No "growth at all costs" metrics</li>
                <li>No forced exit in 5 years</li>
                <li>We build for attorneys, not investors</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                <strong>Result:</strong> You get to build tools that actually help attorneys, not features that drive vanity metrics.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h3>🤝 Co-Ownership Mentality</h3>
            <p>
                Founding Members aren't "customers" — they're co-builders. You're not in customer support. You're building a movement with them.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                <strong>You'll work directly with attorneys</strong> who are fighting insurance companies, not corporate legal departments managing vendor relationships.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Our Culture</h2>
        
        <p>
            <strong>We're not a "work hard, play hard" Silicon Valley startup.</strong>
        </p>
        
        <p>
            We're a team of people who believe solo attorneys deserve the same tools BigLaw and insurance companies have. 
            We're building something remarkable, but we're not burning ourselves out to do it.
        </p>
        
        <ul style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 2.2;">
            <li>✅ <strong>Async-first communication:</strong> Slack/Loom, not 6 hours of Zoom calls. Weekly "Vow Calls" = 30 minutes max.</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>No fake urgency:</strong> Real deadlines (Bar compliance, customer onboarding), not "growth hacking sprints."</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>Family-first:</strong> Kids sick? Take the day. No guilt. We're building for decades, not burning out in 2 years.</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>Transparent decision-making:</strong> Founder shares revenue numbers, strategy, roadmap. No black-box leadership.</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>Attorney-first:</strong> If attorneys hate a feature, we kill it. No ego. No "but we already built it."</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>No recruiters. No ATS black holes.</strong> Email HR directly. Humans read every application.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div class="quote-box" style="border-left-color: #F59E0B; background: #FFF9E6;">
            <p style="color: #78350F;">
                "We bring in people who are not only professionally capable but also morally inspiring. When you share opportunities, knowledge, and kindness, blessings follow in ways we can't imagine."
            </p>
            <p class="quote-author" style="color: #78350F;">— Afghan S. Yasha Ullah Khan, Founder & Chief Vow Keeper</p>
        </div>
        
        <h2>How to Apply</h2>
        
        <p>
            <strong>We're not hiring until Q3 2026</strong> (currently onboarding first 300 Founding Members), but if you're excited about this mission, 
            we want to hear from you <strong>now</strong>.
        </p>
        
        <p style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #0A2463; margin: 32px 0;">
            Send us:
        </p>
        
        <ul style="font-size: 18px;">
            <li><strong>Your resume</strong> (PDF)</li>
            <li><strong>A short note</strong> (200-300 words) answering: <em>"Why do you care about helping solo attorneys fight insurance companies?"</em></li>
            <li><strong>What role</strong> you're interested in (put in subject line: "FSM Rebel", "Compliance Warrior", "Success Warrior", "Growth Rebel", or "Content Warrior")</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-align: center;">
            <a href="mailto:careers@truevow.law?subject=[Role Name] - Early Interest" class="cta-button">
                Email careers@truevow.law →
            </a>
        </p>
        
        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px; color: #999; font-style: italic; margin-top: 24px;">
            We respond within 72 hours. If you're a great fit, we'll add you to our early talent pipeline for Q3 2026.
        </p>
        
        <div style="background: #F8F9FA; padding: 32px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 60px 0; text-align: center;">
            <h3 style="color: #0A2463; margin-bottom: 16px;">💰 $5K Referral Bounty</h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                Know someone perfect for TrueVow? Refer them to <strong>careers@truevow.law</strong>. 
                If they're hired and complete 90 days, you get <strong>$5,000</strong>. No limits. Refer 3 people = $15K.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A2463 0%, #1a3a8a 100%); color: white; padding: 48px; border-radius: 16px; margin: 60px 0; text-align: center;">
            <p style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; color: white;">
                The TrueVow Team Vow
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 20px; color: #E5E5E5; margin-bottom: 0;">
                We take the code. You keep the passion. We win big — together.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px; color: #999; font-style: italic;">
            <strong>P.S.</strong> Not ready to apply? No problem. Bookmark this page and check back in Q2 2026 when we start interviewing.
        </p>
        
    </div>

